02:10.956 --> 02:12.567
- No, it's not that.

02:12.697 --> 02:14.830
It's--

02:14.960 --> 02:16.832
promise me you won't say
anything to Mom and Dad yet.

02:16.962 --> 02:19.139
- Oh, sure.
I promise.

02:19.269 --> 02:21.445
- She and I are flying back out
with National Geographic

02:21.576 --> 02:22.577
