02:26.102 --> 02:27.538
- About three months.

02:27.669 --> 02:30.802
- Oh, fuck you, Jimmy.
You can't do that to me.

02:30.933 --> 02:32.064
I can't be alone with them...
- Keep your voice down.

02:32.195 --> 02:32.804
- for the whole summer.
- Keep your voice down.

02:32.935 --> 02:34.545
- No, I will not keep
my voice down!

02:34.676 --> 02:36.112
I'm fucking pissed at you.

02:36.243 --> 02:37.983
You know how much that sucks?
That really sucks.

02:38.114 --> 02:40.508
Mom and Dad for a whole
summer alone, thanks a lot.

02:40.638 --> 02:42.814
Thanks a lot.
Oh, God.

02:42.945 --> 02:44.512
