07:56.954 --> 07:58.129
Seven and eight.

08:00.044 --> 08:02.873
And clean, sharp.

08:03.004 --> 08:04.701
Smooth it out.
Nice.

08:06.224 --> 08:08.139
Get your leg up, yellow shirt.

08:11.839 --> 08:13.623
Okay.
Nice transition.

08:13.754 --> 08:15.277
And reach.

08:15.407 --> 08:16.974
Thank you.

08:18.498 --> 08:20.108
Nice.
Thanks, everybody.

08:20.238 --> 08:23.024
- Okay, uh,

08:23.154 --> 08:26.288
Patrick, Stacey, Chris, Aubrey,

08:26.418 --> 08:27.985
and Alexia,
you guys stick around.

08:28.116 --> 08:30.292
