decide to do this?

10:00.425 --> 10:01.426
- Well, I don't know.
I've been thinking about it,

10:01.557 --> 10:03.254
you know,
and her and I talked about it.

10:03.385 --> 10:06.170
And I just thought,
if I love her, why wait?

10:06.301 --> 10:08.042
You know, why wait to start
the rest of my life?

10:08.172 --> 10:10.392
So I was thinking about
asking her tonight.

10:10.522 --> 10:12.046
- Her mother's
gonna be so happy.

10:12.176 --> 10:13.613
You know,
she calls all the time asking

10:13.743 --> 10:15.789
