to marry him.

10:29.193 --> 10:31.065
- Is this true?

10:31.195 --> 10:32.849
- Yeah, Dad.
I love her.

10:32.980 --> 10:35.417
- Muchachito, por fin!

10:35.547 --> 10:38.202
[chuckling]
Come here big guy.

10:38.333 --> 10:40.248
Can't tell you
how proud I am of you.

10:40.378 --> 10:42.032
Your mother and I have been
praying for this day

10:42.163 --> 10:44.078
