of you started dating.

10:44.208 --> 10:45.253
When do you plan
on asking her?

10:45.383 --> 10:46.994
- He's gonna ask her tonight.

10:47.124 --> 10:48.735
And he's gonna
use Abuelita's ring.

10:48.865 --> 10:50.998
- Wepa!

10:51.128 --> 10:53.565
