to motivate you to act,

10:55.655 --> 10:56.830
to take control of your--

10:56.960 --> 10:58.005
- Don't start, Victor.

10:58.135 --> 10:59.136
Just go get the ring.

10:59.267 --> 11:01.356
- Por fin!
[laughing]

11:03.227 --> 11:04.620
- Think he's a little happy?

11:04.751 --> 11:06.056
- I can't thank you enough,Matty.

11:06.187 --> 11:07.318
