for the family.

11:26.468 --> 11:28.426
All right.
Now, would you please

11:28.557 --> 11:30.951
feast your eyes on that beauty?

11:31.081 --> 11:33.214
- Arthur,
what the hell is that?

11:33.344 --> 11:35.259
- Pretty great, right?
- No, not--

11:35.390 --> 11:36.304
not at all.

11:36.434 --> 11:38.001
Whose is it,
and why is it here?

11:38.132 --> 11:39.524
